# stdbuf

> Run a command with modified buffering operations for its standard streams
> More information: https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/stdbuf

- Change the stdin buffer size to 512 KiB:

`stdbuf --input={any something} {any something}`

- Change the stdout buffer to line-buffered:

`stdbuf --output={any something} {any something}`

- Change the stderr buffer to unbuffered:

`stdbuf --error={int number: 0} {any something}`
